    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.282511>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Prodorsal shields of the species of Geckobiella. A, G. trombidiiformis; B, G. p e l a e z i; C, G. boneti; D, G. bakeri; E, G. pyriformis; F, G. javieri; G, G. diolii; H, G. donnae sp. nov. Scale bar 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/282511/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.282512>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Geckobiella donnae sp. nov., female. A, gnathosoma dorsal view; B, gnathosoma ventral view; C, Idiosoma dorsum; D, Idiosoma venter. Scale bars 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/282512/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.282513>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Geckobiella donnae sp. nov., female, legs I – IV (trochanters-tarsi). Scale bars 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/282513/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

